    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that's ready to get you from A to B without breaking the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a fantastic opportunity for someone who values functionality and character. While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, it remains a solid, drivable choice with plenty of life left to give!",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and small rock chips consistent with regular driving, while the interior remains in great shape with no major stains or tears. Mechanically, the car is solid, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has received regular oil changes. It is a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that is ready for the road.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies a superior balance of performance and value. This unit has been curated to meet the standards of the discerning driver, featuring a refined interior and a powertrain that remains responsive and reliable. Having undergone a rigorous professional assessment, this vehicle stands as a testament to conscientious ownership. We invite you to experience the sophisticated driving dynamics and proven caliber of this exceptional offering.",
      "price": 33950.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This car has been so good to me and still runs like a total dream! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-cared for over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, it's comfy, clean, and a blast to drive. I'd love for it to go to a great new home, so feel free to reach out if you want to come see it or take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit is mechanically sound, with the critical double-VANOS system recently overhauled and rod bearings replaced with treated shells for long-term reliability. The rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with plates to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. The suspension utilizes refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining precise turn-in and camber control. While the paint displays minor road-rash consistent with its mileage, the powertrain remains in peak operating condition with consistent compression across all six cylinders.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Runs well. Clean title. Regular maintenance records available.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This luxury SUV represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a blend of sophistication and dependable performance. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection will reveal the typical minor stone chips on the front fascia and a few light swirl marks consistent with responsible ownership. The alloy wheels are in great shape, free of significant curb rash. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has never been smoked in; the leather seats are soft and supportive, showing only light creasing on the driver's bolster. All onboard electronics, including the navigation system, premium audio, and heated seats, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers power smoothly through the automatic transmission. It has a documented service history, with recent fluid changes and a fresh inspection ensuring it is road-ready. The tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining, and the brakes feel firm and responsive. This is a solid, honest vehicle that has been cared for and is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sophisticated design. This unit has been subjected to a rigorous professional assessment, ensuring that all systems perform to a high standard of reliability. The exterior retains its refined character, while the interior reflects a consistent history of diligent care. Offering a balanced synthesis of performance and longevity, this automobile represents a distinguished choice for the discerning driver seeking both value and excellence.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    }
